{"tid":2429233,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"考慮梗領養中/大型嘅狗狗入一入嚟","createTime":"2021-03-02T07:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:21:23.000Z","uid":184681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b34b4b5f7e80f3e7cf82743992d50efba01d5e","tid":2429233,"uid":184681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇人有興趣領養1歲女仔拉布拉多呀？<br />\n<br />\n今日有狗狗義工問我可唔可以幫手暫託，但原來將會係第三次轉foster<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如其將狗狗轉嚟轉去，我更希望佢可以搵到forever home<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充多少少資料:<br />\n狗狗比較好動，需要出街2-3次，平時都係出街去廁所<br />\n第1個foster因為要番office所以就唔可以繼續照顧佢<br />\n第2個foster因為狗狗叫聲(轉咗新環境)所以被人投訴，好可惜唔能夠繼續foster<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以去呢條link睇相:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLBXmxTD0Dz/?igshid=1f7k8m8ba5y23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLBXmxTD0Dz%2F%3Figshid%3D1f7k8m8ba5y23&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2d20f82e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLBXmxTD0Dz%2F%3Figshid%3D1f7k8m8ba5y23&h=d8f6595a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLBXmxTD0Dz/?igshid=1f7k8m8ba5y23</a>"},{"pid":"8cec084056faa142200fc49a09d654799a2ae913","tid":2429233,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"搵eric ko馴化咗佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456205b41cc09b8ae7f3b692f00a83bee1cadeae","tid":2429233,"uid":161232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b34b4b5f7e8